151
00:09:47,390 --> 00:09:50,551
Kau tak boleh menggelar diri sebagai Lizardmen lagi.

152
00:09:51,986 --> 00:09:53,953
Halau dia keluar sekarang!

153
00:09:54,410 --> 00:09:56,598
Apa?!

154
00:10:02,190 --> 00:10:03,540
Kau terlupa sesuatu.

155
00:10:04,630 --> 00:10:05,450
Nah.

156
00:10:25,230 --> 00:10:27,599
Gabiru-sama!

157
00:10:28,100 --> 00:10:28,370
Hei!

158
00:10:28,370 --> 00:10:30,100
